剑法的防守招式，以守为攻，后发制人","source_skill":"skill_mo_zi_jian_fa","source_refs":[{"chapter":49,"line_start":224,"line_end":225,"text":"悉心传授他墨子剑法"}]}],"factions":[],"locations":[{"id":"loc_ya_fu_ren_fu","name":"雅夫人府","region":"邯郸","one_line":"赵雅的府邸","source_refs":[{"chapter":49,"line_start":216,"line_end":217,"text":"十一骑旋风般卷进赵雅的夫人府去"}]}],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
{"segment":4,"line_start":281,"line_end":370,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_zhao_ya","speaker_name":"赵雅","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"李牧在战场上是无可比拟的猛将，但在权谋手段上却太鲁莽了，更低估赵穆对王兄的影响力。","tone":"陈述","chapter":49,"line_start":284,"line_end":286},{"speaker":"char_xiang_shao_long","speaker_name":"项少龙","listener":"char_zhao_ya","text":"发生什么事？","tone":"疑问","chapter":49,"line_start":288,"line_end":288},{"speaker":"char_zhao_ya","speaker_name":"赵雅","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"他们不明白王兄自长平一战后，最怕是别人说他犯错，现今李牧摆明要逼王兄承认在妮姊一事中有疏忽和包庇凶嫌之责，他怎肯接受？","tone":"无奈","chapter":49,"line_start":290,"line_end":292},{"speaker":"char_xiang_shao_long","speaker_name":"项少龙","listener":"char_zhao_ya","text":"究竟发生了什么事？","tone":"疑问","chapter":49,"line_start":294,"line_end":294},{"speaker":"char_zhao_ya","speaker_name":"赵雅","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"昨晚宴会后，赵穆立即进宫找王兄，说些什么话没有人知道，想来是指责军方借题发挥，想动摇王兄宝座之语，对你当然亦不会有好说话。","tone":"陈述","chapter":49,"line_start":296,"line_end":298},{"speaker":"char_xiang_shao_long","speaker_name":"项少龙","listener":"char_zhao_ya","text":"你如何答他？","tone":"疑问","chapter":49,"line_start":308,"line_end":308},{"speaker":"char_zhao_ya","speaker_name":"赵雅","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"当然不会说真话，不过看来他仍相信我没有迷上你，或者是因为我以前的声誉太坏了吧！","tone":"苦笑","chapter":49,"line_start":310,"line_end":312},{"speaker":"char_xiang_shao_long","speaker_name":"项少龙","listener":"char_zhao_ya","text":"现时我牵涉到军方和乌家两个系统，你王兄应不敢对我轻举妄动吧！","tone":"陈述","chapter":49,"line_start":314,"line_end":316},{"speaker":"char_zhao_ya","speaker_name":"赵雅","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"人家担心得要死哩！你千万不要高估军方和乌家的力量，假若王兄不顾一切，就地把你处决，那时米已成炊，谁也不会真的为你与王兄正面冲突。","tone":"担心","chapter":49,"line_start":318,"line_end":320},{"speaker":"char_xiang_shao_long","speaker_name":"项少龙","listener":"char_zhao_ya","text":"想杀我项少龙，恐怕孝成王要出动大军才行，我绝不会俯首就擒的。","tone":"冷笑","chapter":49,"line_start":322,"line_end":324},{"speaker":"char_zhao_ya","speaker_name":"赵雅","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"有时你这人似足有勇无谋之辈，只是王兄的亲卫兵团便有二万人，守城兵达三万之众，主帅乐乘又是赵穆的人，有起事来，谁救得了你？你若有不测，人家怎活下去啊！","tone":"焦急","chapter":49,"line_start":326,"line_end":328},{"speaker":"char_xiang_shao_long","speaker_name":"项少龙","listener":"char_zhao_ya","text":"放心吧！曾有人说过我是多灾多难的新圣人，所以绝死不了。","tone":"微笑","chapter":49,"line_start":330,"line_end":332},{"speaker":"char_zhao_ya","speaker_name":"赵雅","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"谁说的？什么是新圣人？现在人家方寸已失，心乱如麻，少龙快教我应该怎样做？","tone":"疑问","chapter":49,"line_start":334,"line_end":336},{"speaker":"char_xiang_shao_long","speaker_name":"项少龙","listener":"char_zhao_ya","text":"还有什么选择，只有逃离邯郸，始有生路。但走前我定要把赵穆碎尸万段，才可泄心头之恨。","tone":"沉声","chapter":49,"line_start":338,"line_end":340},{"speaker":"char_zhao_ya","speaker_name":"赵雅","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"你答应要带雅儿走的啊！","tone":"恳求","chapter":49,"line_start":342,"line_end":342},{"speaker":"char_xiang_shao_long","speaker_name":"项少龙","listener":"char_zhao_ya","text":"这个当然，不但带你走，小盘和倩儿亦随我们走。","tone":"陈述","chapter":49,"line_start":344,"line_end":346},{"speaker":"char_zhao_ya","speaker_name":"赵雅","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"是否到秦国去？唉！秦人比任何一国的人更深沉可怕哩！","tone":"无奈","chapter":49,"line_start":348,"line_end":350},{"speaker":"char_xiang_shao_long","speaker_name":"项少龙","listener":"char_zhao_ya","text":"别忘了我是新圣人。","tone":"调侃","chapter":49,"line_start":352,"line_end":352},{"speaker":"char_xiang_shao_long","speaker_name":"项少龙","listener":"char_zhao_ya","text":"恐怕要到秦国才有机会陪伴你们，孝成王的反应大出我意料之外，我要立即找李牧商量，设法缓和你王兄的情绪。","tone":"陈述","chapter":49,"line_start":352,"line_end":354},{"speaker":"char_zhao_ya","speaker_name":"赵雅","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"我会负责侦察宫内的情况，幸好有晶王后站在你那一边说话，王兄又三心二意，短期内仍不敢以霹雳手段对付你。","tone":"陈述","chapter":49,"line_start":356,"line_end":358}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_zhao_ya","name":"赵雅","alias":["雅儿","雅夫人"],"identity":"赵国夫人","faction":"faction_zhao_guo_chao_ting","role":"companion","archetype":"scholar","rank":"平平无奇","one_line":"赵国夫人，深爱项少龙，为他的安危担忧","personality":{"traits":["美艳","聪慧","深情","善谋","忧郁"],"speech_style":"柔声","temperament":"忧郁"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_xiang_shao_long","type":"恋人","intensity":65,"bond_level":3,"dynamic":"相爱"},{"target":"char_zhao_xiao_cheng_wang","type":"亲属","intensity":50,"bond_level":2,"dynamic":"兄妹"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[49],"source_refs":[{"chapter":49,"line_start":281,"line_end":282,"text":"赵雅神色凝重地回来了"}]},{"id":"char_li_mu","name":"李牧","alias":[],"identity":"赵国名将","faction":"faction_zhao_guo_chao_ting","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"炉火纯青","one_line":"赵国名将，勇猛但不善权谋","personality":{"traits":["勇猛","正直","鲁莽","忠诚","不善权谋"],"speech_style":"直率","temperament":"刚烈"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[49],"source_refs":[{"chapter":49,"line_start":284,"line_end":285,"text":"李牧在战场上是无可比拟的猛将"}]},{"id":"char_zou_yan","name":"邹衍","alias":[],"identity":"齐国学者","faction":null,"role":"npc","archetype":"scholar","rank":"平平无奇","one_line":"齐国学者，称项少龙为新圣人","personality":{"traits":["博学","神秘","有远见","深沉","超然"],"speech_style":"深沉","temperament":"超然"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[49],"source_refs":[{"chapter":49,"line_start":360,"line_end":361,"text":"邹衍可能深信他是什么新圣人"}]},{"id":"char_ying_zheng","name":"嬴政","alias":[],"identity":"秦国质子","faction":null,"role":"npc","archetype":"scholar","rank":"平平无奇","one_line":"秦国质子，未来秦始皇","personality":{"traits":["隐忍","有野心","聪慧","坚毅","深沉"],"speech_style":"沉默","temperament":"深沉"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[49],"source_refs":[{"chapter":49,"line_start":362,"line_end":363,"text":"若有新圣人，就应是嬴政"}]},{"id":"char_le_cheng","name":"乐乘","alias":[],"identity":"赵国守城主帅","faction":"faction_zhao_guo_chao_ting","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"平平无奇","one_line":"赵国守城主帅，赵穆的人","personality":{"traits":["忠诚于赵穆","有军权","谨慎","听命","无主见"],"speech_style":"沉稳","temperament":"服从"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_zhao_mu","type":"主仆","intensity":60,"bond_level":3,"dynamic":"听命"}],"known_s